        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Safe Sponsor Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the placement of an unaccompanied alien child with a proposed custodian who is not a U.S. citizen or a lawful permanent resident. The bill also requires a custodian to post a bond as assurance that the child will attend each necessary immigration-related legal proceeding. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
